metadata.name: Cherry pAi 001
metadata.description:
A limited series of 1 of 1 mixed media photographic collage and digital Ai artworks by accomplished Australian artist AprilYFU, time travelling artist and provocateur. Lovingly crafting works that are beautiful but disarming, with a focus on the sensuality of the female form, sex, love, alternate dimensions and worlds.

2969 x4083
